title: Producer Loops House for Sylenth Vol.1-6581 [deepstatus]

Producer.Loops.House.for.Sylenth.Vol.1





        House  for  Sylenth Vol 1 is the first in a brand new series
        of  products  from Sounds + MIDI. This soundset includes 128
        original  patches  for  Sylenth.  This pack was designed for
        producers  of  House, Electro, Trance, and other styles with
        require   dance  sounds.  It's  packed  full  of  infectious
        sounds,   phrases   and   progressions.   One  of  the  most
        interesting  features about this product is that it includes
        a  set of hugely inspiring and 100% royalty-free MIDI loops,
        for  you to use in your tracks without any additional costs.
                                     
        Inside  youÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ll  find 128 patches for Sylenth 2.21 or higher,
        including  45  powerful  bass  sounds,  45 soaring leads, 16
        pluck  instruments  and  10  rich  chord  &  pad  sounds. In
        addition  to  this, 48 MIDI loops are included. Each file is
        labelled  to  match the correct patch within the patch bank.
        You  can  also  try  them  out  with  any of the 128 patches
        included  to  achieve  your own sound. All patches have been
        programmed  so  the  modulation  wheel on your keyboard will
                       dramatically alter the sounds.
                                     
                           About "Sounds + MIDI":
                                     
        Sounds  +  MIDI bring you the hottest sounds around for your
        EDM  productions  including  loops,  samples, MIDI files and
        synthesizer   soundsets  for  producers  of  House,  Trance,
                 Dubstep, Deep Tech, and other hot styles.
                                     
                            About the MP3 Demos:
                                     
        All   of  the  MIDI  files  included  in  this  product  are
        demonstrated  in  the  MP3 demos. The MP3 demos also include
        drums   and   sound   FX,  which  are  included  purely  for
                          demonstration purposes.
